F32 Smart WiFi Thermostat helps you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to set and query the temperature of Thermostat. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you thermostat - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your MAGNUM Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “Heat Link” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure F32 Smart WiFi Thermostat devices in “Heat Link” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “Heat Link” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “Heat Link” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Heat Link” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, What is the temperature of the thermostat?"
“Alexa, Set the thermostat to 20 degrees."
